def_en: Feminine qualities and things relate to or are considered typical of women, in contrast to men.

def_cn: 女子气的;女人味的;(尤指)柔美的
def_en: Someone or something that is feminine has qualities that are considered typical of women, especially being pretty or gentle.

def_cn: (名词、代词或形容词)阴性的
def_en: In some languages, a feminine noun, pronoun, or adjective has a different form from a masculine or neuter one, or behaves in a different way.
